flowchart TD
  A[LinkedIn job page] --> B[job-scraper-chrome]
  A2[Hiring Cafe search page] --> C[page-hook.js captures /api/search-jobs]
  C --> B

  B --> D[POST /jobs/ingest]
  D --> E[job-pipeline-service]

  E --> F[(job_postings)]
  E --> G[(prompt_library)]

  F --> H[n8n classification workflow]
  H --> I[POST /jobs/classify/run]
  I --> E

  E --> J[job_postings.classification_key]
  J --> K[application generation]
  K --> L[(job_applications)]

  L --> M[n8n legacy scoring workflow]
  M --> N[POST /jobs/score/run]
  N --> E

  E --> O{Application score passes threshold?}
  O -- Yes --> P[Tracker sync]
  O -- Yes --> Q[POST /applications/{id}/notify]
  Q --> E
  O -- No --> R[Remain scored only]

  S[Legacy GET /jobs/hiringcafe route\nPlaywright capture] -. optional / fallback .-> E
